<h1>Hello <%= @resource.first_name %>!</h1>

<p>Someone has requested to change your password. You can do this by clicking the button below.</p>

<%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), class: "button" %>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
